OL,3,CWoman denies killing five-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl by scalding her in bath in 1978
OL,6,FA 66-year-old woman has denied killing
OL,7,Fa five-year-old child by scalding her
OL,8,Fin a hot bath in 1978.
OL,10,FJanice Nix was charged in February
OL,11,Fover the death of Andrea Bernard, who
OL,12,Fwas taken to hospital after she
OL,13,Fsuffered burns in Thornton Heath,
OL,14,Fsouth London, on June 6 1978, the
OL,15,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,17,FAndrea was treated at a hospital in
OL,18,FCroydon before being transferred to a
OL,19,Fspecialist burns unit in East
OL,20,FGrinstead, West Sussex, but died from
OL,21,Fher injuries on July 13 that year.
