OL,3,CWoman denies killing five-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl by scalding her in bath in 1978
OL,6,FThe defendant, of Rodenhurst Road,
OL,7,FClapham, south-west London, appeared
OL,8,Fat the Old Bailey on Wednesday where
OL,9,Fshe denied one count of manslaughter.
OL,11,FShe also denied another charge
OL,12,Frelating to alleged cruelty to
OL,13,FAndrea's brother Desmond Bernard
OL,14,Fbetween October 1 1975 and June 6
OL,15,F1978, when he was eight.
OL,17,FThe defendant was aged between 16 and
OL,18,F19 at the time of the alleged
OL,19,Fincidents.
