OL,3,CWoman denies killing five-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl by scalding her in bath in 1978
OL,6,FA previous hearing at Uxbridge
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court heard that on June
OL,8,F6 1978, Andrea had been forced into a
OL,9,Fvery hot bath which scalded 50% of her
OL,10,Fbody.
OL,12,FThe Metropolitan Police said the force
OL,13,Flaunched an investigation into
OL,14,FAndrea's death in September 2022.
OL,16,FThe court heard the incident was
OL,17,Freported to police at that time by Mr
OL,18,FBernard, who is now an adult.
